# OpenClaw — Cursor rules

Project rules live in **.cursor/rules/** (modern .mdc setup). Cursor loads them automatically.

- **Understand the project:** Read **ANTIGRAVITY.md** to understand the project; keep it updated whenever you make relevant changes.
- **Hardware / devices:** Read **DetailHardware.md** for hardware and device info; keep it updated whenever hardware or device setup changes.
- **Always applied:** `project-context.mdc`, `agents-config.mdc`
- **When editing TS/TSX:** `typescript-standards.mdc`
- **When editing Docker/config:** `docker-runtime.mdc`

For full agent and ops discipline, read **AGENTS.md** and **.antigravityrules**.
